1
00:00:00,010 --> 00:00:02,470
<i>[Alarm: 5:30 a.m.]</i>

2
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:07,890
Was that all a dream?

3
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:10,330
<i>You should go to Shanghai.</i>

4
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:13,260
<i>It sounds like a great opportunity.</i>

5
00:00:13,260 --> 00:00:14,140
<i>What?</i>

6
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:18,560
<i>I can't see myself falling in love with you.</i>

7
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:21,140
<i>No, it wasn't.</i>

8
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:23,620
<i>I was undeniably rejected.</i>

9
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:28,580
<i>Now I still must live with Nishijima Itsuka under these circumstances.</i>

10
00:00:28,580 --> 00:00:30,840
This is too awkward...

11
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:40,790
Who gave you permission to camp out here?

12
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:43,810
It'll only be until I find a new place.

13
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:49,840
<i>Sister Nao...</i>

14
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:53,300
<i>I'm leaving this place.</i>

15
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:57,790
I've made my choice. I have no right to use that room anymore.

16
00:00:57,790 --> 00:01:00,010
You're free to quit or whatever,

17
00:01:00,010 --> 00:01:02,390
but you better not slack as caretaker

18
00:01:02,390 --> 00:01:04,020
while you're still here.

19
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:08,360
<i>Timing and subtitles brought to you by
